      "content": "i know people say that stuff but it doesnt feel real. i dont have anyone here. no friends, no family nearby, just work and this tiny apartment. if i just stopped showing up, it would take weeks for anyone to even check in. it's not even sad anymore, it's just... true. there's no footprint.",
